@startuml
actor User

note over User
프로그램 시작 시 User 객체가 생성된다고 가정합니다.
end note

== 프로그램 시작 ==
User -> AppController : start()
AppController -> OutputView : printWelcome()\n(인사 / 선택 목록 출력)

== 로그인 메뉴 선택 ==
User -> AppController : select(로그인)

AppController -> InputView : read("닉네임 입력")
InputView --> AppController : nickname

== 로그인 처리 ==
AppController -> MemberService : findByNickname(nickname)
activate MemberService

alt 멤버 존재
    MemberService -> MemberRepository : findByNickname(nickname)
    activate MemberRepository
    MemberRepository --> MemberService : Member
    deactivate MemberRepository

    MemberService --> AppController : Member
    deactivate MemberService

    AppController -> OutputView : printLoginSuccess(Member)

    == 로그인 성공 후 ==
    AppController -> MeetingService : getTomorrowMeetings(member)
    activate MeetingService
    MeetingService -> MeetingRepository : findByParticipant(member)
    activate MeetingRepository
    MeetingRepository --> MeetingService : List<Meeting>
    deactivate MeetingRepository

    MeetingService --> AppController : List<Meeting>
    deactivate MeetingService

    AppController -> OutputView : printTomorrowMeetings()

else 멤버 없음
    MemberService -> MemberRepository : findByNickname(nickname)
    activate MemberRepository
    MemberRepository --> MemberService : null
    deactivate MemberRepository

    MemberService --> AppController : IllegalArgumentException("[ERROR] 존재하지 않는 멤버")
    deactivate MemberService

    AppController -> OutputView : printError("[ERROR] 존재하지 않는 멤버입니다.")
end

== 메뉴로 돌아가기 ==
AppController -> OutputView : printWelcome()\n(선택 목록 재출력)

== 종료 ==
User -> AppController : select(종료)
AppController -> OutputView : printExit()

@enduml
